➜株洲建宁港：臭水已逝黑水变清 再现青春靓丽容颜
http://www.sohu.com/a/430605810_100180399	26080
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201109/2f9bfeb3988d4501bb431cebfa130c95.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">建宁港黑臭水体治理改造施工现场。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201109/a3e1b390528a431da96ed19f27afa327.png" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">建宁港黑臭水体治理改造施工现场。</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201109/8eeb45bfdcc64315ab7a300bce1c4f19.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
